snippet.title: Sengoku Dynasty - Official Trailer | Guerrilla Collective 2023 Showcase
snippet.description:
Watch the latest trailer for Sengoku Dynasty to see various locations, gameplay showcasing building and survival elements, daily life activities, and more from this upcoming game that is a mix of open-world RPG, builder and colony sim, life simulation and survival gameplay, set in feudal Japan. Sengoku Dynasty will be available on PC.

#GameTrailers #SoG #Gaming
